name: Christmas Guarantee: Upgrade to Special Delivery
description: Ordering from 18th - 20th December 2013? We can still get your order to you in time for Christmas! Special Delivery is a Next Working day service- which is guaranteed to arrive before 1pm (to 99% of addresses in mainland UK) and will require a signature on delivery. Order are usually dispatched within 24 hours of us receiving them- so please allow for this when placing your order. We'll do our best to get your order shipped on the same day, if humanly possible! Please note- orders placed on a Thursday & Shipped on Friday will not arrive until Monday. If you require Saturday delivery, get in touch. For quantities upwards of this, drop me a line at shop@nikkimcwilliams.com and I'll do my best to help. ***PLEASE NOTE: This service is available to mainland UK occupants only.***
